dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for Brown County, Wisconsin in 2009. [The Brown County Planning Commission conducts a countywide land use inventory every decade. Fieldwork for the most recent inventory was completed in June 2001 and updated periodically since. Using this data, the various land use categories were generalized, broken down by acreage.The existing land use feature class is a compiled version of all the land use inventory done during the comprehensive planning phases (2001-2007).]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.browncountywi.gov/departments/planning-and-land-services/land-information-office/
